resources.string: At Grey Rock Casino, we offer the following gaming-related services: Over 190 slot machines Two electronic tables (Roulette and Blackjack) Bingo Hall Totem Rewards Club where members can earn Totem Reward points Poker Room open Thursday and Friday from 6 PM and Saturday and Sunday from 3 PM Make sure to check out our ongoing promotions! The Grey Rock Valley View Restaurant, located on the second floor of the Casino! Open 7 days a week 2 PM to 10 PM with a variety of favourites on the menu. Come experience Grey Rock on another level!
